headline: Innova SD39 SD-Consultant Now Available at AutoZone
summary: Innova Electronics Corporation, a leading supplier of test equipment and diagnostic reporting for the automotive aftermarket, today announced the launch of its SD39 SD-Consultant. The new flagship of the Innova Smart Diagnostic series, the SD39 is now available at AutoZone, with additional auto parts retailers expected to carry it later this year.
